00:29:48.486 --> 00:29:52.406
to go. I'll try to be practical and specific because I know this audience

522
00:29:52.446 --> 00:29:54.126
is working on these questions in real time.

523
00:29:56.126 --> 00:29:59.826
So AI is being used across every phase of the drug product life cycle, and the

524
00:29:59.846 --> 00:30:03.096
