00:30:10.806 --> 00:30:13.966
design. In the non-clinical research, we're seeing AI applied to

528
00:30:13.986 --> 00:30:17.476
pharmacokinetics and pharmacodynamics modeling and toxicology studies.

529
00:30:18.146 --> 00:30:21.986
In clinical research, AI is being used for dose finding, site

530
00:30:22.066 --> 00:30:22.676
selection,

531
00:30:23.506 --> 00:30:25.026
patient recruitment and retention,

532
00:30:26.406 --> 00:30:29.926
data collection and management, real world data analyses, patient

533
00:30:29.966 --> 00:30:32.606
recruitment, and clinical endpoint assessment.

534
00:30:33.286 --> 00:30:35.306
And in the manufacturing and post-marketing setting,

535
00:30:36.746 --> 00:30:40.566
